StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.name: [GetFormInstances]
StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.body:
( @LeadID uniqueiden..er ) AS
SET TRANSACTION ISOLATION LEVEL READ UNCOMMITTED
SELECT [LeadFormID], [LeadID], f.[FormID], [FormName], CASE WHEN lf.[FormID] is null THEN 0 ELSE 1 END as [IsComplete] FROM [dbo].[Form] f LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[LeadForm] lf ON lf.FormID = f.FormID AND [LeadID] = @LeadID
